# Lifevault Backend

Environment variables (copy to .env):

```
PORT=3001
TURSO_DATABASE_URL=file:./data/lifevault.db
TURSO_AUTH_TOKEN=
JWT_SECRET=your-secret-key-change-in-production

# Google Calendar OAuth
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=
GOOGLE_REDIRECT_URI=http://localhost:3001/api/sync/google/callback

# Stripe (subscriptions & payments)
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=
STRIPE_PRICE_MONTHLY=price_monthly_id
STRIPE_PRICE_YEARLY=price_yearly_id
STRIPE_PRICE_LIFETIME=price_lifetime_id
STRIPE_PRICE_TEMPLATE=price_template_id
```

## Commands

```bash
npm run dev      # Start dev server with hot reload
npm run build    # Build for production
npm run start    # Start production server
npm run migrate  # Run database migrations
```

## API Endpoints

### Auth
- `POST /api/auth/signup` ‚Äî Register new user
- `POST /api/auth/login` ‚Äî Login, returns JWT
- `GET /api/auth/me` ‚Äî Get current user profile (auth required)

### Tasks
- `GET /api/tasks` ‚Äî List tasks (filter by status/category/priority)
- `POST /api/tasks` ‚Äî Create task
- `GET /api/tasks/:id` ‚Äî Get task
- `PATCH /api/tasks/:id` ‚Äî Update task
- `DELETE /api/tasks/:id` ‚Äî Delete task
- `POST /api/tasks/rollover` ‚Äî Auto-roll pending overdue tasks

### Events
- `GET /api/events` ‚Äî List events (filter by calendar/date range)
- `POST /api/events` ‚Äî Create event
- `GET /api/events/:id` ‚Äî Get event
- `PATCH /api/events/:id` ‚Äî Update event
- `DELETE /api/events/:id` ‚Äî Delete event

### Calendars
- `GET /api/calendars` ‚Äî List calendars
- `POST /api/calendars` ‚Äî Create calendar
- `PATCH /api/calendars/:id` ‚Äî Update calendar
- `DELETE /api/calendars/:id` ‚Äî Delete calendar

### Expenses
- `GET /api/expenses` ‚Äî List expenses (filter by category/date/recurring)
- `POST /api/expenses` ‚Äî Create expense
- `GET /api/expenses/:id` ‚Äî Get expense
- `PATCH /api/expenses/:id` ‚Äî Update expense
- `DELETE /api/expenses/:id` ‚Äî Delete expense
- `POST /api/expenses/generate-recurring` ‚Äî Generate recurring expense instances
- `GET /api/expenses/stats/summary` ‚Äî Expense totals/averages
- `GET /api/expenses/stats/by-category` ‚Äî Expenses grouped by category

### Google Calendar Sync
- `GET /api/sync/google/auth-url` ‚Äî Get Google OAuth URL
- `POST /api/sync/google/callback` ‚Äî Handle OAuth callback (exchange code for tokens)
- `GET /api/sync/google/status` ‚Äî Check connection status
- `POST /api/sync/google/disconnect` ‚Äî Disconnect Google Calendar
- `POST /api/sync/push-event/:eventId` ‚Äî Push event to Google Calendar
- `POST /api/sync/pull-events` ‚Äî Pull events from Google Calendar
- `POST /api/sync/full-sync` ‚Äî Full bidirectional sync

### Apple Calendar (CalDAV) Sync
- `POST /api/apple-calendar/connect` ‚Äî Connect Apple Calendar (server URL + app password)
- `GET /api/apple-calendar/status` ‚Äî Check connection status
- `POST /api/apple-calendar/disconnect` ‚Äî Disconnect Apple Calendar
- `GET /api/apple-calendar/calendars` ‚Äî Discover available calendars
- `POST /api/apple-calendar/pull` ‚Äî Pull events from Apple Calendar
- `POST /api/apple-calendar/push-event/:eventId` ‚Äî Push event to Apple Calendar
- `POST /api/apple-calendar/full-sync` ‚Äî Full bidirectional sync

### Subscriptions (Stripe)
- `GET /api/subscriptions/config` ‚Äî Get pricing plans
- `POST /api/subscriptions/create-checkout` ‚Äî Create subscription checkout session
- `POST /api/subscriptions/buy-template` ‚Äî Purchase template
- `GET /api/subscriptions/my-plan` ‚Äî Get current plan and features
- `POST /api/subscriptions/webhook` ‚Äî Stripe webhook endpoint

### Templates
- `GET /api/templates` ‚Äî List templates
- `GET /api/templates/:id` ‚Äî Get template details
- `POST /api/templates/:id/download` ‚Äî Download template (increments counter)

### Links
- `GET /api/links` ‚Äî List links
- `POST /api/links` ‚Äî Create link
- `DELETE /api/links/:id` ‚Äî Delete link

### Notes
- `GET /api/notes` ‚Äî List notes
- `POST /api/notes` ‚Äî Create note
- `PATCH /api/notes/:id` ‚Äî Update note
- `DELETE /api/notes/:id` ‚Äî Delete note